TextEng: I have a letter from Oleff. He sent me.
Text: 올레프의 편지를 가져왔습니다. 그분이 저를 보냈습니다.

TextEng: Me have Oleff letter. He sent me heres?
Text: 올레프 편지 가져왔어. 그분이 날 보냈어.

TextEng: Goodbye.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Yous can tell me. It be okay.
What do you know of the plague?
What can you tell me about these tombs?
Text: 이 무덤들에 대해 무엇을 알려 주실 수 있습니까?

TextEng: Have you heard of anything odd? Any rumors?
You know anything about the bad plague?
What you can tell me about tombs?
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
Text: 이상한 일이나 소문 들은 거 있어?

TextEng: You know about cure attempts maybe?
What do you know about attempts at a cure?
Text: 치료법을 찾으려는 시도에 대해 무엇을 아십니까?

TextEng: What is this place?
What this place?
Who is Oleff?
Who Oleff?
Farewell.
Bye bye.
What have you learned from this tomb?
What you learn from this tomb?
Where are the other tombs located?
Where other tombs located?
Did you find any artifacts in here?
You finds artifact stuffs in here?
I have other questions.
Me gots other questions and stuff.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can tell me. Come on.
We share the calling of cleric. You can tell me.
Text: 우리 둘 다 성직자잖습니까. 말씀해 주시죠.

TextEng: We's both kinda cleric. Yous can tell me.
Text: 우리 둘 다 성직자잖아. 말해 줘.

TextEng: What a good looker like yous got to hide, hmm?
Text: 그렇게 아름다우신 분이 뭘 숨기고 계시길래요?

TextEng: A handsome man like you needs to keep secrets?
Text: 그렇게 잘생기신 분이 굳이 비밀을 지켜야 합니까?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Did this contribute to their deaths from the plague?
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 이것이 역병으로 인한 그들의 죽음에 한몫한 겁니까?
